)BODY
%TUTORIAL -----------TRANSMIT/RECEIVE UTILITY : OVERVIEW  ------------ T
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD
%
+   The TRANSMIT/RECEIVE utility provides the capability to electronical
+  transfer data (datasets and/or messages) between the ABL, SALTLAKE, a
+  WILMINGTON mainframe computers.  Transmitted data is then received by
+  the targeted user(s) on the destination computer. A log file of TRANS
+  RECEIVE activity is automatically maintained, providing a convenient
+  means of monitoring and referencing transmitted data.
+
+   Messages appearing on your screen prefixed "INM" provide information
+  relating specifically to TRANSMIT/RECEIVE processing.
+
+
+Press%PF3+to exit this screen
)PROC
)END
